Hello! I'm Shinesprite41, but you can call me Shine! Here are some of the achievements I'm proud of:

=== Random Achievements: === * Beat Erika with All Challenges enabled without using ANY eggs or fossils
* Beat Bugsy with All Challenges enabled while only breeding to obtain new mons (no grinding out dragonites with Dragon Eggs)
* Calculated Minimum Attack for the [[Gyms]] page === [https://www.speedrun.com/user/Shinesprite41 Speedrun Achievements:] === * 2nd Place holder in Solo-Player Normal Clicking Solo-Player Tutorial
* WR holder in Solo-Player AutoClicker Tutorial
* WR holder in Solo-Player Clickless Tutorial
* WR holder in Solo-Player CODED Normal Clicking Tutorial
* WR holder in Solo-Player CODED AutoClicker Tutorial
* WR holder in Solo-Player CODED Clickless Tutorial
* WR holder in 2-Player Co-Op Normal Clicking Kanto Champion w/ ZardAce1
* WR holder in 4-Player Co-Op Clickless Tutorial w/ myself 4 times
* 2nd Place holder in Solo-Player Normal Clicking Kanto Champion
